author: djames
msg: Fix the Python tests to work on Windows, by updating our file:// URLs to
contain the right number of slashes. (If there are too many slashes, the
URL doesn't work, and an is_canonical assertion failure pops up.)
(REPOS_URL): Calculate REPOS_URL from REPOS_PATH. Add two extra slashes
to the start of the URL if they're not already present.
test_open_ra_session): Don't calculate self.repos_url from REPOS_PATH.
